happen is is a little bit of more of the same i think 
that the united that the banking system itself is

40:13.493 --> 40:39.197
to blame for a lot of what's happened uh i know 
personally people that were in brazil soliciting

40:13.493 --> 40:39.197
the brazilian government to take additional 
loans at very attractive interest rates

