42:10.583 --> 42:16.551
fact, we at General Motors encouraged our 
executives and almost insisted that they bring

42:10.583 --> 42:16.551
their families. We felt that an executive with his 
family could do a much better job because of the

42:19.769 --> 42:30.781
degree of stability that continuing family life 
