42:19.769 --> 42:30.781
what mama was doing with the house in Connecticut 
or something. Is there much social mixing with the

42:30.801 --> 42:40.832
local population or do the Americans tend to 
socialize with each other as happens in military

42:30.801 --> 42:40.832
bases quite often? A difficult question to answer 
with just one answer. Some Americans associate

42:44.305 --> 42:50.952
only with Americans and always will because they 
feel comfortable with something that they're

42:44.305 --> 42:50.952
very, very familiar with. But the vast majority of 
them, us, associated with the local population.

