Very, very close friends in the Brazilian, 
Argentine, Uruguayan, Chile community, in my

42:57.119 --> 43:01.683
case. We had no problems with the language, liked 
the people, and discovered that that was really

43:03.145 --> 43:12.675
the way that we got a lot more out of the time that we 
spent in the country. so that I would say the vast

43:13.246 --> 43:21.889
majority of Americans really make an effort to get 
