44:42.758 --> 44:47.344
degree of... of terrorism, kidnapping, 
assassinations. The president of Fiat was

44:50.961 --> 44:53.063
assassinated, for example. Three executives, 
one American and two Argentine executives of the

44:55.445 --> 45:01.210
Ford Motor Company were assassinated. It puts a 
lot of pressure on family life. You become a lot

45:03.453 --> 45:04.874
more careful. You live under constant security. 
