45:12.101 --> 45:16.605
I think most of the families that I knew came 
through stronger than ever before as a result of

45:16.973 --> 45:19.877
their experiences. Once you came through it, it 
was something that you could point to with pride

45:19.937 --> 45:25.163
for the rest of your life. I've met people from 
those times since, and they're very, very proud of

45:25.244 --> 45:31.512
what happened to them there. Okay.

